data.description: LUXURY AWAITS! Almost like buying a newly constructed home and better--this one is flawless and FULLY landscaped! Nestled in Mountain Hawk, every inch of this 4-bed, 2-bath haven is elegant. State-of-the-art kitchen with built-in appliances, expansive island with bar seating, farm sink, and conveniently adjacent dining space. Seamless flow between kitchen/dining/living with bountiful natural light. Plus a master suite paradise! Dual sinks, spacious tiled shower, and large walk-in. Top-notch finishes throughout, modern tile, plush carpet, and easy-to-maintain yard ensure you live in style with zero hassle. Enjoy the city lights and warm summer nights under your covered patio, zip over to a local eatery or take a bike ride in this well-kept neighborhood.
